title: Validate with the Manage  permission , User is able to add key value pair when no existing header insertion profile is present
custom_steps:
1. Create RBACv3 role with Manage only access for header insertion Page
2. Assign a role to a new user.
3. Login with user.
4. Click on  Settings -> Manage -> header insertion
5. Edit in the Settings -> Manage -> header insertion
custom_expected:
1. User is able to view and create a new header insertion profile
2. User is able to edit existing header insertion profile in the page.
3. Audit log should be seen on making changes or creating a new header insertion profile
